in a 117-95 victory Sunday win over the road-weary Philadelphia 76ers. Vlade
Divac had 14 points, 11 rebounds and 11 assists for his sixth career
triple-double and Chris Webber added 26 points, 10 rebounds and eight assists.
</P>
