apply for American visas Monday at the U.S. Interests Section in Havana, the
American mission here.
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
Refining Prostate Testing Will Help
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO (AP) -- Doctors may be able to reduce false alarms when
