<HEADLINE> Wall Street Opens Mixed; Dow Up 16  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stock prices opened mixed on Monday. The Dow
Jones Industrial Average is up 16 points in early trading.
Advancing issues on the New York Stock Exchange hold a 3-to-2 lead
over decliners.
</P>
<P>
   The Nasdaq Composite Index is off 88 points and the Standard &AMP;
Poor's 500 Stock Index is fractionally higher.
</P>
