<HEADLINE> 'Brockovich' Retains Top Spot  </HEADLINE>
By TOM HARRIGAN, Associated Press Writer
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- ''Erin Brockovich,'' the legal drama starring
